General.Name: Cedar Woods Properties Ltd
General.Description: Cedar Woods Properties Limited engages in property investment and development activities in Australia. It is involved in the acquisition, development, marketing, and sale of housing lots, apartments, townhouses, and commercial properties in Western Australia, South Australia, Victoria, and Queensland. The company was incorporated in 1987 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
